{"tid":1954600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食環署外判清潔工涉販毒被捕","createTime":"2020-04-02T03:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T03:24:13.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc67eb51984dd109b309434a826d8916dc97545","tid":1954600,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzVVLXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzVVLXD.jpg&h=80c0090c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方於長洲碼頭拘捕一名男子，涉嫌販毒。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n水警刑事部根據線報及調查，連日在長洲碼頭埋伏，至凌晨約兩時，待一名目標男子由中環乘船抵達後，於碼頭外進行拘捕，搜出約30克懷疑冰毒，市值約2萬元。該名58歲姓馮男子涉嫌販毒被捕，現正被扣留調查。據知他任職食環署外判清潔工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200402/KZNUKEQB6JH66TBOVJPOZABYYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200402%2FKZNUKEQB6JH66TBOVJPOZABYYY%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUj%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=192a20b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200402%2FKZNUKEQB6JH66TBOVJPOZABYYY%2F&h=0813967d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200402/KZNUKEQB6JH66TBOVJPOZABYYY/</a>"},{"pid":"5b5c124baaed335b6e79864cb25fd826cde68773","tid":1954600,"uid":214644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />掃地只係興趣，真正身份係毒販"},{"pid":"c450e7414453a8c3107814ecf70b16ddc2b50ebf","tid":1954600,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b5c124baaed335b6e79864cb25fd826cde68773","tid":1954600,"uid":214644,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />掃地只係興趣，真正身份係毒販"},"citedBy":0,"replyT